com.intel.device.api.sensor

Class SensorCalibrationConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.device.api.sensor.SensorCalibrationConfig

  • @Immutable
 @NotThreadSafe
public class SensorCalibrationConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    The class defining sensor calibration information as it comes from the device. The data structures have different values when being transferred to / from the wearable so two different classes are used to reflect this difference. See SensorCalibrationConfig for sending calibration requests to the wearable.
